    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2003 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and benefits from recent double VANOS servicing and a valve clearance adjustment. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates and upgraded trailing arm bushings to ensure structural rigidity during high-lateral load cornering. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the performance envelope remains sharp, supported by a well-damped suspension and responsive steering rack. A driver-focused example that prioritizes drivetrain excellence and tactile feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
